{
  "stem": "17299.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 94.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to a fellow, we could have some salami too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, there's no chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to weigh it out, and there's nothing left over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told him, you ever heard of putting a couple of pails of water in it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Overnight, the salami will absorb all the water on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you got your salami?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's how I got our first salami.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later on, they moved the kitchen out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they built a new camp in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We moved in that kitchen also, a new kitchen and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to steal from-- sorry to say-- from other prisoners to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish prisoners, and Gentile also later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the kapos, which we are all Gentile, had special food, better than what the Jews had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were stealing from the kapos also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Though I worked in food magazine, I was the only German Jew in the food magazine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rest were Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got along fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But only one thing was bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that happened before I came in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the day of Yom Kippur, 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Hungarian Jews went to the SS and told the SS, tomorrow is Yom Kippur, the day of fast.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Will you shut down the water and not give out any food for 24 hours so that we all can celebrate the day of Yom Kippur?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we guarantee you that the work performance will not suffer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the SS took that with a smile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food was given out for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No water to wash or to drink either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the work performance had not to suffer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how many bodies and unconscious got carried in the camp afterwards, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
